{"title":"JM的未命名","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["2020小学期"],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1233#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/submissions?problem_id=1233","statistics":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1233/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1233/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/discussion/problem/1233"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"序列中初始只有一个非负整数 $n$ ，将序列中满足 $x > 1$ 的数不断拆分为 $\\lfloor x/2 \\rfloor$ , $x \\% 2$ , $\\lfloor x/2 \\rfloor$ 三个数并置于原位，最终得到一个仅含 $0, 1$ 的序列。求这个最终序列中 $[l, r]$ 区间内有多少个 $1$ 。序列下标从 $1$ 起，且假定下标 $l, r$ 合法。\r\n\r\n多组询问。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行一个整数$T$，为询问的组数。\r\n\r\n接下来$T$行，每行三个整数$n,l,r$，含义如上。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出一行一个非负整数表示答案。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```plain\r\n2\r\n6 2 4\r\n8 1 10\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```plain\r\n2\r\n5\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1 \\leq T \\leq 10^5$\r\n\r\n$0 \\le n \\le 2^{60}$\r\n\r\n$1 \\le l,r \\le 10^{18}$"}]}